  <description>A new Nara Industries automatroid - the Driver - built on the Soldat chassis from The Dead Man's Switch.

The Driver is a light, versatile support mechanoid that:
  * Wields basic sidearms (autopistols and revolvers) through the Fortified weapon framework.
  * Can be gestated at the DMS mech gestator and controlled by a mechanitor.
  * Is cleared to operate Vehicle Framework vehicles - it can drive tanks and crew vehicle turrets (requires the included C# compatibility patch, which lifts Vehicle Framework's hard block on colony mechanoids operating vehicle roles, for this mech only).

Based on the Soldat mechanoid from "The Dead Man's Switch". Load this mod after DMS, Vehicle Framework and Harmony.

Requires: Biotech, Fortified Feature Framework, The Dead Man's Switch, Vehicle Framework, Harmony.</description>
